import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Paper, List, ListItem, ListItemText } from '@mui/material';

const Experience: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ py: 4 }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
        Experience
      </Typography>

      <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 3, mb: 3 }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
          Software Developer Intern (Angular)
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
          Pratian Technologies, Bengaluru, India | September 2023 â€“ February 2024
        </Typography>
        <List>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemText primary="Developed and optimized the front-end of a web application using Angular." />
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemText primary="Collaborated with cross-functional teams to ensure responsive design and client satisfaction." />
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemText primary="Ensured website performance and optimization across various devices." />
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemText primary="Conducted testing and used analytics tools to evaluate and improve user experience." />
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </Paper>

      <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 3, mb: 3 }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
          Skill Development Course
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
          NTTF College, Bengaluru, India | November 2024
        </Typography>
        <List>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemText primary="Completed a certification course in the MERN stack and AWS." />
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemText primary="Gained hands-on experience in MERN stack development." />
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem>
            <ListItemText primary="Developed a deeper understanding of AWS cloud services." />
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </Paper>

      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
        Education
      </Typography>

      <Paper elevation={3} sx={{ p: 3 }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
          Bachelor of Technology (BTech) in Computer Science
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
          Glocal University, Uttar Pradesh, India | 2023
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1">CGPA: 7.4</Typography>
      </Paper>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Experience;
